Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛 這胸針真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和花名很速配
